WEBVTT


00:00:03.406 --> 00:00:05.680
It leads a European environmental policy

00:00:05.720 --> 00:00:08.560
This is a set of measures taken by the European Union to protect

00:00:08.640 --> 00:00:10.720
our environment and fight against ecological problems

00:00:11.120 --> 00:00:11.720
Among these measures

00:00:11.721 --> 00:00:14.721
we find for example the reduction of greenhouse gas emissions

00:00:15.040 --> 00:00:17.560
and the promotion of renewable energy use

00:00:17.640 --> 00:00:19.920
European environmental policy is based on tools

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:21.160
such as financial incentives,

00:00:21.360 --> 00:00:23.480
awareness programs and standards

00:00:23.764 --> 00:00:25.389
it aims to ensure sustainable development

00:00:25.390 --> 00:00:26.905
taking into account economic, 

00:00:26.905 --> 00:00:28.270
political and social issues

00:00:28.617 --> 00:00:29.709
If this video helped you, 

00:00:29.709 --> 00:00:30.256
drop a like, 

00:00:30.256 --> 00:00:31.097
share and subscribe!
